14:42.674 --> 14:44.592
Hey, so listen,
I hooked a real Shamu,

14:44.676 --> 14:46.553
and need to lay off
some of the action.

14:46.636 --> 14:47.637
Who's the whale?

14:47.679 --> 14:49.055
If you don't mind,

14:49.139 --> 14:50.056
I'd rather lay
the details on you

14:50.140 --> 14:51.975
faccia a faccia.

14:53.351 --> 14:54.769
It's face to face. Sorry.

14:54.853 --> 14:56.521
I was trying something.

14:56.604 --> 14:58.189
Didn't work.

15:01.735 --> 15:04.154
Hey, gentlemen.

15:04.195 --> 15:06.072
-Hey, Walt.
-Walt.

15:06.156 --> 15:09.367
Thank you for meeting me
on such short notice.

15:09.451 --> 15:10.744
No problem.

15:10.827 --> 15:12.662
I took the liberty of ordering
a couple martinis.

15:12.704 --> 15:14.205
Hope that's okay.

15:14.247 --> 15:17.667
Eugene, we're gonna need
a very tall seafood tower.

15:17.709 --> 15:20.045
-Make my nose bleed.
-Very good, Mr. Dinty.

15:20.128 --> 15:21.713
All right. Thanks, bud.

15:21.755 --> 15:22.922
Please tell me no allergies.

15:23.006 --> 15:24.549
-No, we're fine.
-(groans)

15:24.632 --> 15:26.801
I got a stepsister, she
even looks at a shrimp cocktail,

15:26.885 --> 15:28.553
blows up like a balloon.

15:28.595 --> 15:30.055
We almost lost her
on prom night.

15:30.138 --> 15:32.307
-We're good.
-(chuckling) Okay, okay.

15:32.390 --> 15:33.975
So, what brings you up the 405?

15:34.059 --> 15:36.227
Oh, okay. Right to it.
Huh? No lube?

15:36.269 --> 15:37.562
RAY:
Jesus. How are you?

15:37.645 --> 15:39.105
How are the kids?
They grow up so fast.

15:39.189 --> 15:40.315
Come on now.

15:40.398 --> 15:41.858
Okay!

15:41.900 --> 15:45.111
I got a guy looking to bet
a hundred grand a game,

15:45.195 --> 15:47.364
maybe three, four times a week.

15:47.405 --> 15:50.408
400 grand, maximum exposure.

15:50.492 --> 15:51.618
We'd cover two.

15:51.701 --> 15:54.120
Uh... you know,
let's-let's play it safe

15:54.204 --> 15:56.581
and say 500, 250 each?

15:56.664 --> 15:58.040
That's safe?

15:58.083 --> 15:59.376
My sphincter could
bend steel right now.

15:59.417 --> 16:01.127
I mean, if it's too rich
for you guys,

16:01.211 --> 16:03.004
-I totally understand.
-Don't condescend.

16:03.088 --> 16:04.297
Well, then don't wet
your panties.

16:04.381 --> 16:05.924
Why isn't your guy
betting in Vegas?

16:06.007 --> 16:08.259
He certainly could get
a free room at those numbers.

16:08.301 --> 16:09.594
WALT:
Because he's smart.

16:09.636 --> 16:11.721
Huh? No paper trail,
there's no taxes.

16:11.763 --> 16:13.139
What else do you know about him?

16:13.223 --> 16:14.891
WALT:
Well, let's see.

16:14.933 --> 16:16.726
He is of the Asian persuasion.

16:16.768 --> 16:18.353
Not that that matters,
I'm colorblind.

16:18.436 --> 16:20.939
He has factories in Cambodia

16:20.980 --> 16:23.149
that make high-end sneakers.

16:23.233 --> 16:25.735
There may be children
on the assembly lines,

16:25.777 --> 16:26.778
I do not ask.

16:26.820 --> 16:29.155
Uh, moved here in 2009,

16:29.239 --> 16:30.949
and financed a bunch
of slasher films

16:30.990 --> 16:35.328
so he can meet young ingenues
of the Caucasian persuasion.

16:36.538 --> 16:38.456
That enough?
You guys need more?

16:38.498 --> 16:40.834
-Yeah, is he any good?
-(forced laugh)

16:40.917 --> 16:42.293
Well, he thinks he is.

16:42.377 --> 16:44.379
That's all that really
matters, am I right?

16:46.172 --> 16:47.757
(sighs)

16:47.799 --> 16:49.634
You know, we'd have to agree
on the point spread

16:49.718 --> 16:51.302
before we take any bets.

16:51.386 --> 16:53.805
-Yeah, yeah, of course.
-What if instead of paying us,

16:53.847 --> 16:56.224
he decides to jump on a plane
and disappear?

16:56.307 --> 16:58.476
Well, that would be
very disappointing, right?

16:58.560 --> 17:01.563
But what if he loses
16 weeks in a row

17:01.646 --> 17:03.273
and we all retire?

17:04.023 --> 17:07.152
Talk to me.
How's your sphincter?

17:08.653 --> 17:09.863
WALT:
Whoa!

17:09.945 --> 17:11.573
I hope none of you guys
are keeping Kosher.

17:11.656 --> 17:13.700
You guys mind if I get
a quick shot of this?

17:13.782 --> 17:15.117
I'll make it a vid.

17:15.160 --> 17:17.244
You guys mind
if I get a vid of this?

17:19.955 --> 17:22.334
-I'm home.
-(drops keys)

17:24.711 --> 17:26.338
Anybody?

17:26.421 --> 17:28.631
What's the fuck
with these candles?

17:35.847 --> 17:37.265
What are you doing?

17:38.016 --> 17:39.267
What are you doing?

17:39.351 --> 17:41.436
I was setting the mood.

17:42.896 --> 17:44.314
Oh.

17:45.523 --> 17:47.233
How do you like my new bag?

17:47.317 --> 17:50.278
Well, it's not the first thing
I noticed, but...

17:50.362 --> 17:52.405
-Yeah.
-(chuckles)

17:54.115 --> 17:56.534
Anthony's on Discord.

18:00.413 --> 18:01.456
(grunts)

18:04.959 --> 18:07.087
I'm guessing
you got the purse at Neiman's?

18:07.170 --> 18:08.213
(mouth full):
Saks.

18:08.254 --> 18:09.547
(grunts)
You're welcome.

18:09.589 --> 18:11.633
No. "Saks."

18:11.716 --> 18:13.551
Oh. Saks.

18:13.635 --> 18:14.844
Nice.

18:14.886 --> 18:17.138
(phone vibrating)

18:18.056 --> 18:20.016
Don't.

18:20.058 --> 18:21.518
It's Ray.

18:21.559 --> 18:23.061
-Could be important.
-Think it through, Danny.

18:23.144 --> 18:25.730
You're right, you're right.
(exhales)

18:25.772 --> 18:27.273
Carry on.

18:29.025 --> 18:31.152
-(vibrating continues)
-(grunts)

18:31.236 --> 18:32.862
-(recorded): Hi, this is Danny.
-(water running)

18:32.904 --> 18:34.239
-Go.
-Aw, fuck.

18:36.700 --> 18:38.493
(sighs): I'm sorry, Walt,
I can't get him.

18:38.576 --> 18:40.829
(sighs) Game's kicking off
in five minutes.

18:40.912 --> 18:42.414
I need an answer.

18:42.497 --> 18:43.415
See this?

18:43.498 --> 18:45.750
I used to live here.

18:46.543 --> 18:48.795
-We're in.
-Balls the size of Montana.

18:48.878 --> 18:50.672
-I love it!
-(line disconnects)

18:50.714 --> 18:53.133
(breathing heavily)

18:53.925 --> 18:55.802
(exhales sharply)

18:55.885 --> 18:57.804
Sweet Jesus in heaven,

18:57.887 --> 19:00.849
I never ask you for much,
but I'm asking you for this.

19:00.932 --> 19:04.728
Please let the Broncos lose
by at least six.

19:04.769 --> 19:05.812
What are you doing?

19:05.895 --> 19:07.856
Praying.

19:07.939 --> 19:09.691
Is everything okay?

19:09.774 --> 19:10.817
(sighs)

19:10.900 --> 19:11.818
No.

19:11.901 --> 19:13.445
Oh, baby.

19:13.486 --> 19:15.196
Hang on. I got something
that'll make you feel better.

19:15.280 --> 19:17.115
-What?
-I'm gonna make you some tea.

19:17.157 --> 19:18.450
No caffeine, right?

19:18.533 --> 19:19.325
No.

19:19.409 --> 19:21.369
Wouldn't do that to you.

19:22.454 --> 19:24.122
You can check your phone now.

19:24.205 --> 19:25.623
-You sure?
-(chuckles)

19:25.707 --> 19:27.709
Unless you got another round
in the chamber.

19:27.792 --> 19:28.710
Yeah. I do not.

19:28.793 --> 19:29.711
(giggles)

19:29.753 --> 19:31.463
I'll be right back.

19:32.213 --> 19:33.757
Maybe in the morning?

19:33.798 --> 19:35.842
(footsteps departing)

19:41.139 --> 19:42.098
I got to go!

19:42.140 --> 19:43.558
Thanks for the blow job!

19:43.641 --> 19:45.852
-(indistinct chatter)
-(cheering over TVs)

19:53.610 --> 19:55.153
Rayfield.

19:55.195 --> 19:56.988
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

19:58.948 --> 20:00.450
Rayfield?!

20:01.659 --> 20:03.370
Rayfield!

20:05.413 --> 20:07.207
Oh, look, there's your brother.

20:07.290 --> 20:08.208
Danny!

20:08.291 --> 20:09.668
Hey!

20:09.709 --> 20:11.252
Oh, thank God.

20:11.336 --> 20:12.337
What was the spread?

20:12.379 --> 20:14.005
Oh, I want to say...

20:14.047 --> 20:15.256
six.

20:15.340 --> 20:17.842
-You want to?
-Danny, go easy.

20:17.926 --> 20:21.179
-♪ Easy like Sunday morning. ♪
-(chuckling)

20:21.221 --> 20:22.514
The fuck's wrong with you?

20:22.597 --> 20:24.265
I thought
you liked that old corny shit.

20:24.349 --> 20:25.183
Are you high?

20:25.225 --> 20:26.059
Am I high?

20:26.142 --> 20:27.018
You're high.

20:27.060 --> 20:28.019
He's high.

20:28.103 --> 20:29.479
Oh. Well,

20:29.521 --> 20:32.565
was he high
when he committed us to $200,000

20:32.649 --> 20:35.235
on a Monday
fucking Night Football game?!

20:35.318 --> 20:36.486
I don't know. Let me ask him.

20:36.528 --> 20:38.363
-Ray, honey?
-Huh?

20:38.405 --> 20:40.198
Were you high
when you took the bet?

20:40.240 --> 20:41.282
What bet?

20:41.366 --> 20:42.367
Oh, fuck.

20:42.409 --> 20:43.868
(whispers):
Oh, fuck.

20:44.869 --> 20:47.038
I have so many children.

20:48.832 --> 20:50.542
(birds chirping)

20:50.625 --> 20:53.086
Fucking field goal kicker.

20:53.169 --> 20:54.462
I could have him killed.

20:54.546 --> 20:55.714
-(chuckles): That's funny.
-Good one.

20:55.797 --> 20:57.090
Uh-uh.

20:57.173 --> 20:59.384
-Mm-mm.
-$440,000.

20:59.426 --> 21:00.635
