21:00.719 --> 21:01.428
No, sir.

21:01.511 --> 21:02.679
I'd kind of like to...

21:02.721 --> 21:03.888
Uh-uh-uh-uh.

21:03.972 --> 21:05.390
Okay.

21:06.683 --> 21:08.601
Excuse me, is that one
of those Mille watches?

21:08.685 --> 21:10.937
Yes. These are very expensive.

21:11.021 --> 21:13.940
I bought it from a crazy Jew
for $180,000, cash.

21:14.024 --> 21:14.983
