21:20.864 --> 21:22.574
Go make yourself
crackers and cheese.

21:22.657 --> 21:24.576
-Okay?
-You know I don't eat wheat.

21:24.659 --> 21:27.120
Okay, then just the cheese!
Get out!

21:27.203 --> 21:28.329
(scoffs)

21:28.413 --> 21:29.789
Dick.

21:31.291 --> 21:32.959
