21:33.043 --> 21:35.712
She gets eaten by a clown.

21:35.754 --> 21:37.797
Ooh...

21:37.881 --> 21:40.258
JACK:
Okay. Uh... (sighs deeply)

21:40.300 --> 21:41.926
Monday night--

21:41.968 --> 21:43.428
I like the Texans to win,
straight up.

21:43.470 --> 21:44.596
Money line.

21:44.679 --> 21:45.597
Same bet?

21:45.680 --> 21:47.849
Let's go 500, large.

21:49.893 --> 21:52.270
