they're a nine-point underdog?

21:52.354 --> 21:54.105
I know! I study, okay?!

21:54.147 --> 21:55.732
I know more than you!

21:56.524 --> 21:58.401
Okay, uh, just to be clear,

21:58.443 --> 21:59.778
straight up to win.

21:59.861 --> 22:01.613
