22:01.654 --> 22:03.406
plus 50 grand on the vig.

22:03.448 --> 22:04.699
Uh, no-no vig.

22:04.783 --> 22:06.868
-Wait, hold on...
-No vig!

22:11.539 --> 22:13.124
Are you okay with this?

22:14.125 --> 22:15.251
Y...
(coughs)

22:15.293 --> 22:16.252
Yeah.

22:16.294 --> 22:17.295
Yes.

22:17.379 --> 22:18.630
-(clears throat)
-Okay.

22:18.672 --> 22:20.256
-(coughs)
-A-And if-- and if you win

22:20.298 --> 22:21.966
the big dog...

22:23.134 --> 22:25.095
...we owe you, uh...

22:26.304 --> 22:28.390
...$1.4 million,

22:28.473 --> 22:29.641
give or take.

22:29.724 --> 22:31.309
I'm good for my end, baby.

22:31.393 --> 22:32.644
You good for yours?

22:35.021 --> 22:36.815
(quietly):
How's your sphincter?

22:37.607 --> 22:38.650
-JACK: Hey.
-Huh?

22:38.692 --> 22:39.818
